intertemporal consumption path.

00:53:03.500 --> 00:53:08.467
The guy subject to this sort
of incentive moral hazard

00:53:08.467 --> 00:53:10.300
constraint, they're
actually going to end up

00:53:10.300 --> 00:53:11.740
