01:17:35.830 --> 01:17:38.280
to move very fast.

01:17:38.280 --> 01:17:41.880
You're going to balance
off the incentives

01:17:41.880 --> 01:17:46.170
of today's consumption
versus tomorrow's wealth.

01:17:46.170 --> 01:17:48.570
Wealth moves a little bit,
