01:17:49.230 --> 01:17:50.980
But you don't want it
to move a whole lot.

01:17:50.980 --> 01:17:55.350
Because if it did, that's
the bulk of your utility.

01:17:55.350 --> 01:17:56.430
That's kind of very--

01:17:56.430 --> 01:17:59.640
